source.name: Recorded Parcel Geography with Transaction Date History (Zippped Shapefile Format)
source.description: Recorded parcel geography, both active and retired, with date recorded parcel was added, date recorded parcel was dropped/retired, date was added, dropped or altered re map layer.  Contains geography created since the inception of the basemap in 1995, with some exceptions.
